categories: Category:Alliance to Restore the Republic Special Forces units

nodes.text: Team 19 was an Alliance Special Forces unit attached to the 14th Roving Line during the Galactic Civil War. It was led by Miko Beski. Team 19 was made up of SpaceOps personnel, heavy weapons specialists and a technical squad consisting of transportation, medical and Scanner Communications Operators scan-com specialists. It acted as the 14th Roving Lines main boarding party and planetary assault force. An Aegis combat shuttle served Team 19 on its missions.
Members of Team 19 included Lieutenant Miko Beski, Lieutenant Whumparrin, and protocol droid C-7NO.
